Package: libbroadvoice1
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: library to support BroadVoice16/32 codecs
 This package contains the BroadVoice 16 and 32 low bit rate speech codecs.
 .
 This package contains the shared library.

Package: libbroadvoice-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libbroadvoice1 (= ${binary:Version})
Description: library to support BroadVoice16/32 codecs - development headers
 This package contains the BroadVoice 16 and 32 low bit rate speech codecs.
 .
 This package contains the static library and development headers.

